"understand it. You can expect that …"

msgctxt "mn5:5.8"
msgid "so arāgo adoso amoho anaṅgaṇo asaṅkiliṭṭhacitto kālaṃ karissati."
msgstr "they will die with an uncorrupted mind."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:6.1"
msgid ""
"Tatrāvuso, yvāyaṃ puggalo anaṅgaṇova samāno ‘natthi me ajjhattaṃ aṅgaṇan’ti "
"yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti, tassetaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—subhanimittaṃ manasi "
"karissati, tassa subhanimittassa manasikārā rāgo cittaṃ anuddhaṃsessati;"
msgstr ""
"Take the case of the person who doesn’t have a blemish but does not "
"understand it. You can expect that they will focus on the aspect of beauty, "
"and because of that, lust will infect their mind."

msgctxt "mn5:6.2"
msgid "so sarāgo sadoso samoho sāṅgaṇo saṅkiliṭṭhacitto kālaṃ karissati."
msgstr ""
