#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.27"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:8.1"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ kho, āvuso moggallāna, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenimesaṃ dvinnaṃ puggalānaṃ "
"sāṅgaṇānaṃyeva sataṃ eko hīnapuriso akkhāyati, eko seṭṭhapuriso akkhāyati."
msgstr ""
"This is the cause, this is the reason why, of the two persons with a "
"blemish, one is said to be worse and one better."

msgctxt "mn5:8.2"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ panāvuso moggallāna, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenimesaṃ dvinnaṃ puggalānaṃ "
"anaṅgaṇānaṃyeva sataṃ eko hīnapuriso akkhāyati, eko seṭṭhapuriso "
"akkhāyatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And this is the cause, this is the reason why, of the two persons without a "
"blemish, one is said to be worse and one better.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:9.1"
msgid "“Aṅgaṇaṃ aṅgaṇanti, āvuso, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, the word ‘blemish’ is spoken of."

msgctxt "mn5:9.2"
msgid "Kissa nu kho etaṃ, āvuso, adhivacanaṃ yadidaṃ aṅgaṇan”ti?"
msgstr "But what is ‘blemish’ a term for?”"

msgctxt "mn5:9.3"
msgid ""
"“Pāpakānaṃ kho etaṃ, āvuso, akusalānaṃ icchāvacarānaṃ adhivacanaṃ, yadidaṃ "
"aṅgaṇan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, ‘blemish’ is a term for the spheres of bad, unskillful wishes."

# Both MS and BB are unclear as to the speaker here. BB’s section 9 attibutes the proceeding phrases to sariputta. But surely the question is an interjection by Moggallana, as indicated by the punctuation in MS. However, to start a new speaker here, as MS does, is to suggest that this passage is spoken by Moggallana, which is surely incorrect. The close -ti in the previous segment must simply indicated a quoted term.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:10.1"
msgid ""
"“Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘āpattiñca vata āpanno assaṃ, na ca maṃ bhikkhū jāneyyuṃ āpattiṃ āpanno’ti."
msgstr "‘If I commit an offence, I hope the mendicants don’t find out!’"

msgctxt "mn5:10.3"
msgid "Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ taṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū jāneyyuṃ:"
msgstr "But it’s possible that the mendicants do find out that that mendicant"

msgctxt "mn5:10.4"
msgid "‘āpattiṃ āpanno’ti."
msgstr "has committed an offence."

msgctxt "mn5:10.5"
msgid "‘Jānanti maṃ bhikkhū āpattiṃ āpanno’ti—"
msgstr "Thinking, ‘The mendicants have found out about my offence,’"

msgctxt "mn5:10.6"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr "they get angry and bitter."

msgctxt "mn5:10.7"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr "And that anger and that bitterness"

msgctxt "mn5:10.8"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr "are both blemishes."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:11.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘āpattiñca vata āpanno assaṃ, anuraho maṃ bhikkhū codeyyuṃ, no "
"saṅghamajjhe’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If I commit an offence, I hope the mendicants accuse me in private, not in "
"the middle of the Saṅgha.’"

msgctxt "mn5:11.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ taṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū saṅghamajjhe "
"codeyyuṃ, no anuraho."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that the mendicants do accuse that mendicant in the middle "
"of the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "mn5:11.4"
msgid "‘Saṅghamajjhe maṃ bhikkhū codenti, no anuraho’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:11.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:11.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:11.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:12.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:12.2"
msgid ""
"‘āpattiñca vata āpanno assaṃ, sappaṭipuggalo maṃ codeyya, no "
"appaṭipuggalo’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If I commit an offence, I hope I’m accused by an equal, not by someone who "
"is not an equal.’"

msgctxt "mn5:12.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ taṃ bhikkhuṃ appaṭipuggalo codeyya, "
"no sappaṭipuggalo."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that someone who is not an equal accuses that mendicant …"

msgctxt "mn5:12.4"
msgid "‘Appaṭipuggalo maṃ codeti, no sappaṭipuggalo’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:12.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:12.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:12.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya13"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.28"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:13.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:13.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata mameva satthā paṭipucchitvā paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ "
"deseyya, na aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ satthā paṭipucchitvā paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ "
"dhammaṃ deseyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, I hope the Teacher will teach the mendicants by repeatedly questioning "
"me alone, not some other mendicant.’"

msgctxt "mn5:13.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ satthā paṭipucchitvā "
"paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseyya, na taṃ bhikkhuṃ satthā "
"paṭipucchitvā paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseyya."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that the Teacher will teach the mendicants by repeatedly "
"questioning some other mendicant …"

msgctxt "mn5:13.4"
msgid ""
"‘Aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ satthā paṭipucchitvā paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ "
"deseti, na maṃ satthā paṭipucchitvā paṭipucchitvā bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ "
"desetī’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:13.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:13.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:13.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:14.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:14.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata mameva bhikkhū purakkhatvā purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya paviseyyuṃ, "
"na aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū purakkhatvā purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya "
"paviseyyun’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, I hope the mendicants will enter the village for the meal putting me at "
"the very front, not some other mendicant.’"

msgctxt "mn5:14.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū purakkhatvā "
"purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya paviseyyuṃ, na taṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū purakkhatvā "
"purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya paviseyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that the mendicants will enter the village for the meal "
"putting some other mendicant at the very front …"

msgctxt "mn5:14.4"
msgid ""
"‘Aññaṃ bhikkhuṃ bhikkhū purakkhatvā purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya pavisanti, na "
"maṃ bhikkhū purakkhatvā purakkhatvā gāmaṃ bhattāya pavisantī’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:14.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:14.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:14.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:15.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:15.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata ahameva labheyyaṃ bhattagge aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ, na "
"añño bhikkhu labheyya bhattagge aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍan’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, I hope that I alone get the best seat, the best drink, and the best "
"alms-food in the refectory, not some other mendicant.’"

msgctxt "mn5:15.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ añño bhikkhu labheyya bhattagge "
"aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ, na so bhikkhu labheyya bhattagge aggāsanaṃ "
"aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that some other mendicant gets the best seat, the best "
"drink, and the best alms-food in the refectory …"

msgctxt "mn5:15.4"
msgid ""
"‘Añño bhikkhu labhati bhattagge aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍaṃ, nāhaṃ "
"labhāmi bhattagge aggāsanaṃ aggodakaṃ aggapiṇḍan’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:15.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:15.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:15.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:16.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:16.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata ahameva bhattagge bhuttāvī anumodeyyaṃ, na añño bhikkhu bhattagge "
"bhuttāvī anumodeyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I hope that I alone give the verses of gratitude after eating in the "
"refectory, not some other mendicant.’"

msgctxt "mn5:16.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ añño bhikkhu bhattagge bhuttāvī "
"anumodeyya, na so bhikkhu bhattagge bhuttāvī anumodeyya."
msgstr ""
"But it’s possible that some other mendicant gives the verses of gratitude "
"after eating in the refectory …"

msgctxt "mn5:16.4"
msgid ""
"‘Añño bhikkhu bhattagge bhuttāvī anumodati, nāhaṃ bhattagge bhuttāvī "
"anumodāmī’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:16.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:16.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:16.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya17"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.29"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "mn5:17.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā "
"uppajjeyya:"
msgstr "It’s possible that some mendicant might wish:"

msgctxt "mn5:17.2"
msgid ""
"‘aho vata ahameva ārāmagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseyyaṃ, na añño bhikkhu "
"ārāmagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘Oh, I hope that I might teach the Dhamma to the monks, nuns, laymen, and "
"laywomen in the monastery, not some other mendicant.’"

msgctxt "mn5:17.3"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ añño bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ "
"dhammaṃ deseyya, na so bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:17.4"
msgid ""
"‘Añño bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ deseti, nāhaṃ ārāmagatānaṃ "
"bhikkhūnaṃ dhammaṃ desemī’ti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:17.5"
msgid "iti so kupito hoti appatīto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:17.6"
msgid "Yo ceva kho, āvuso, kopo yo ca appaccayo—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:17.7"
msgid "ubhayametaṃ aṅgaṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya18-20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
