msgctxt "mn5:18-20.3"
msgid "upāsakānaṃ dhammaṃ deseyyaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:18-20.4"
msgid ""
"upāsikānaṃ dhammaṃ deseyyaṃ, na añño bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ upāsikānaṃ dhammaṃ "
"deseyyā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn5:18-20.5"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ añño bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ upāsikānaṃ "
"dhammaṃ deseyya, na so bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ upāsikānaṃ dhammaṃ deseyya."
msgstr "But it’s possible that some other mendicant teaches the Dhamma …"

msgctxt "mn5:18-20.6"
msgid ""
"‘Añño bhikkhu ārāmagatānaṃ upāsikānaṃ dhammaṃ deseti, nāhaṃ ārāmagatānaṃ "
